#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Cpublication-repositories.md:1
msgid "Publication Repositories"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Cpublication-repositories.md:3
msgid ""
"The CPRMV API supports four publication methods, each registered in `data/"
"cprmvmethods.ttl` under the `cprmvmethods:analysismethods` or "
"`cprmvmethods:formalisationmethods` collection. The method detection logic "
"in `serve.py` (`detect_cprmv_serve_acknowledged_method`) walks these RDF "
"lists and attempts to parse the incoming rule set identifier against the "
"`cprmv-serve:normalized-id-format` pattern of each method."
msgstr ""

